data.title: Rail roko to protest against slum demolition in Mumbai's Dombivli
data.meta_description: MUMBAI: Over 500 people living in slums near Dombivli railway station protested against demolition of illegal slums by staging a rail roko on Thursday afternoon distrupting India Rail Info is a Busy Junction for Travellers & Rail Enthusiasts.
